headline: It’s Time to Pare Your Stock Losers. This Simple Strategy Can Help.
summary: In the beginning, hedge fund managers have the experience and clients have the money.  At the end, clients have the experience and hedge fund managers have the money.  It’s hard to remember a time in the markets that was harder to analyze, yet there’s a bull market in expert advice even as thoughtful people are pondering President Donald Trump’s efforts to change the framework that has governed commerce since World War II.
